{
  "stem": "3165.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- it could have been that somebody came to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to know if anybody has some relatives in the States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew I had an aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember Aunt Shaindl, Mimi Shaindl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remembered-- I didn't know her last name, but I remembered her maiden name, which was the same as my mother's maiden name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which was Feldman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they told me where to go to show-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to tell the people from New York-- from the Jewish Congress-- about survivors.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told somebody in the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A personnel lady-- or man, whoever-- took the information, gave them a picture of a me and Susan-- my sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told them that I have an aunt in the States, and her name is Shaindl Feldman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we gave her our names, the survivors, where we're from, everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sure enough, they put it in the Jewish paper-- New York Jewish paper, whatever it was called.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and so what happened-- and my auntie lived in Boston, and she would take the New York Jewish paper-- the Yiddish paper.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, sure enough, she reads in the paper, and she sees our names and our picture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she got in contact, I guess, with the Jewish Congress where we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she started to write to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how we found that first-- about my auntie in Boston.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then the Jewish Congress was very nice, from New York.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they would send us parcels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for some reason, they had my name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I would get parcels from them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I still remember, there was a bathing suit there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
